data.title: Kamen Rider Geats: PREMIUM DX Memorial Oneness Raise Buckle Official Images Revealed
data.meta_description: Here are the official images of the PREMIUM DX Memorial Oneness Raise Buckle from the Kamen Rider Geats summer movie.
data.text:
Premium Bandai posted the official images of the PREMIUM DX Memorial Oneness Raise Buckle from the Kamen Rider Geats: The Four Aces and the Black Fox film.

Originally released as a campaign item for the DX Gotchardriver or the DX Gotchardriver & Gotchardraw Holder Set, this release is an updated version of the original DX version with the item now being painted in metallic red, thus giving it a luxurious appearance. It also has a new voice activation button and a back switch was also added, thus allowing a smooth activation of the newly recorded voice lines.

The release also comes with the Kamen Rider Geats (Oneness Ver.) Ride Chemy Card as well as a Legend Parallel Rare version of said card. That said, the included additional voice lines are: Ace Ukiyo (both the regular and his split versions), Keiwa Sakurai, Neon Kurama, Azuma Michinaga, Win Hareruya, Sae Ganaha, Ittetsu Tanba, Tsumuri, and Ziin.

This Premium Bandai web exclusive set cost 4,950 yen, and is set for a February 2025 release. Pre-orders will end on December 1st.
